posts.title: Go Yoon Jung
posts.description:
Go Youn-jung is a South Korean actress and model. She made her acting debut in the television series He Is Psychometric and gained recognition for her supporting role in the Netflix production Sweet Home. Wikipedia
Born: April 22, 1996 (age 28 years), Mullae-dong, Seoul, South Korea
Movies: Hunt

Agent: MAA
